data.description: Susquehanna Township Gem !!!   This fabulous  4-5 bedroom ranch home with energy efficient  gas hot water heat and updated central air.  The roof was installed in 2021 and rubber roof installed in 2023.  Driveway was widened to a 2 car width  to allow for more parking and rear yard was fenced in with 6' high fence.  The large  living room has  hardwood floors and a wood burning fireplace . Adjacent to  the Living room is the dining room and then a large country kitchen with built in kitchen table.  Kitchen was upgraded with white cabinets and has a gas cooktop and 2 ovens for all your cooking and baking needs.  There is an oversized laundry room off of the kitchen complete with washer,  dryer and cabinetry to store laundry supplies with counter to fold clothes. There are 4 bedrooms on the first floor and the master bedroom has a large closet outfitted with a closet system.  Hardwood floors under carpet in 3 bedrooms. The lower level contains a great room and a bonus room that can be used as a bedroom.  There is a full bath in the lower level.   One car garage with electric opener. The house is located close to UPMC hospital and their periphery medical buildings.
